verbose_text: Compared with the model group, tempol (100 muM) and Rg1 (5 and 10 muM) treatments significantly reduced the release of IL-1beta and IL-18 in supernatants from the H 2 O 2 -treated hippocampal neurons (XREF_FIG; P < 0.05).
evidence: Rg1 (5 and 10 muM) treatments significantly reduced the release of IL-1beta
